@{b}Registering Vapor Software@{ub}
**************************

Thank you for supporting Amiga Software Development! By registering the
Software you use, you ensure further development of high quality Amiga
applications!


 @{" How To Use " Link "How To Use"}          How to use the registration utility
 @{" Registration Sites " Link "Registration Sites"}  Information on registration sites
 @{" Manually " Link "Manually"}            Registering without the registration utility
 @{" Problems " Link "Problems"}            If you have any problems...
 @{" Support " Link "Support"}             How to get support and updates

- Other stuff: -

